                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant H</hi> 8.) I stopped the prisoner with this bag of coffee, in Essex-street, Whitechapel, about eleven o'clock in the morning—there was another roan with him, whom we took, but he made his escape—the prisoner said he received it of that man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
